Some people arrive at us with a romantic vision and head in the clouds and, when they realize they have to come to rehearsals twice a week, take the preparatory classes and spend a lot of time on the roads for concerts, they quickly lose their enthusiasm.
But it works the same way in every group that wants to work and achieve goals.
The Tap Tap Group currently has 20 members.
